  ***************************************************************************  
                                  Summary  
  ***************************************************************************

    This is an .ISO copy of the MIMS New Ethical (New Zealand) CD used 
    extensively by medical, pharmacy, nursing, midwifery students and
    professionals throughout New Zealand (with overlapping content for
    Australian users).

    MIMS comes in 3 parts (called books):

    (1) Drug interactions - where two or more drugs can be selected to
    test their interactions
    (2) MIMS New Zealand - where specific drug information is found
    (3) References - extra resources and tools


    The retail cost of this product is: NZ$336 (~ US$240) per year


    Version: February 2010 (new updates released biannually)  



    THIS IS A VERY RARE PROGRAM, SO PLEASE SEED TO KEEP IT ALIVE!

    IF THERE ARE ANY CRACKERS ABLE TO, PLEASE PROVIDE A PROPER CRACK
    FOR THIS!

    PLEASE POST OTHER MEDICAL/PHARMACEUTICAL RELATED CONTENT ON TPB FOR
    THE ENJOYMENT OF ALL! - CHECK MY UPLOADS FOR MORE EDUCATIONAL RESOURCES



  ***************************************************************************
                                 Installation                                   
  ***************************************************************************

    (1) Mount/burn the .ISO with daemon tools 
    (http://www.daemon-tools.cc/eng/downloads)
    (2) Select and install "MIMS Desktop" version (not the network
    version)


    Because this .ISO is their expired February 2010 edition, you will
    need to download and use "RunAsDate" to internally change the date of
    the program, downlad this from:
   <a href=" http://www.nirsoft.net/utils/run_as_date.html" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://www.nirsoft.net/utils/run_as_date.html</a>


    (3) Follow the installation instructions on the RunAsDate website and
    install
    (4) Select the MIMSdesk.exe program for the "Application to run" field
    of RunAsDate 

    Usual location of MIMSdesk.exe is:
    C:Program FilesCMPMedicaNew ZealandMIMSdesktop


    (5) In the "Date/time" field, select any day in April 2010 and any time
    (but do not use the 12AM default time)
    (6) Keep "Parameters" field empty and keep "move time forward" ticked
    (7) Name and create a RunAsDate shortcut if you wish
    (8) Run program and enjoy!!
